or even claimed that.

195
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,072
It's just
something people say.

196
00:07:21,074 --> 00:07:23,542
Really?

197
00:07:23,544 --> 00:07:25,310
Now you tell me.

198
00:07:25,312 --> 00:07:27,779
(sarcastic chuckle)
Water prevents cramps.

199
