and fuels you better than water.

232
00:08:34,114 --> 00:08:36,615
'Cause the more water you drink,
the better you feel.

233
00:08:36,617 --> 00:08:37,916
<i>Drink more water!</i>

234
00:08:37,918 --> 00:08:40,252
These companies have
consistently portrayed

235
00:08:40,254 --> 00:08:42,354
dehydration
as a serious threat

236
00:08:42,356 --> 00:08:46,191
for one, simple reason--
it gets us to drink more.

237
