The International
Bottled Water Association

238
00:08:48,595 --> 00:08:50,662
publishes
a hydration calculator

239
00:08:50,664 --> 00:08:53,431
that can recommend you drink
two liters of water a day.

240
00:08:53,433 --> 00:08:55,500
